# SKILL.md must be kept in sync

`SKILL.md` (repo root) and `skills/nooks/SKILL.md` must always be **exact copies** for cross-platform compatibility — some agent runtimes load from the root, others from `skills/<name>/`.

Whenever you edit one, immediately copy the change to the other. Never leave them out of sync.
